# Claude Code Configuration — Autosmartweby

## Source of Truth

- **GitHub repo je jediny source of truth** pro veskerou konfiguraci, kod a dokumentaci.
- **Apps Script editor NENI source of truth.** Kod se meni v repo (apps-script/), po merge se pushne pres clasp.
- **Google Sheets je source of truth pro runtime data** (LEADS sheet), NE pro logiku nebo konfiguraci.

## Task Workflow (POVINNE)

Kazdy task MUSI:
1. Zmenit kod (pokud je to code task)
2. Aktualizovat prislusne kanonicke docs (podle stream mapy nize)
3. Vytvorit nebo aktualizovat task record v `docs/30-task-records/`
4. Spustit generovani: `node scripts/docs/build-changelog.mjs && node scripts/docs/build-task-registry.mjs`
5. Spustit validaci: `node scripts/docs/check-doc-sync.mjs`

### Na konci KAZDEHO tasku spust:
```bash
node scripts/docs/build-changelog.mjs
node scripts/docs/build-task-registry.mjs
node scripts/docs/check-doc-sync.mjs
```

### Novy task record:
```bash
node scripts/docs/create-task-record.mjs <TASK_ID> "<TITLE>"
```

## Branch Naming

- `task/A1-short-name` — stream A (Data & Automation)
- `task/B4-short-name` — stream B (Infrastructure & Offer)
- `task/C2-short-name` — stream C (Business Process & Prioritization)

## Task-Doc Mapa

### Stream A — Data & Automation
Primarni docs:
- docs/20-current-state.md
- docs/23-data-model.md
- docs/24-automation-workflows.md

### Stream B — Infrastructure & Offer
Primarni docs:
- docs/20-current-state.md
- docs/22-technical-architecture.md
- docs/26-offer-generation.md
- docs/27-infrastructure-storage.md

### Stream C — Business Process & Prioritization
Primarni docs:
- docs/20-current-state.md
- docs/21-business-process.md
- docs/24-automation-workflows.md
- docs/25-lead-prioritization.md

### Vzdy povinne
- Task record v docs/30-task-records/
- docs/20-current-state.md (pokud se meni stav systemu)

## Zakazy

- NEEDITUJ soubory v docs/archive/ pokud task neni explicitne o archivnich dokumentech
- NEEDITUJ rucne docs/11-change-log.md ani docs/29-task-registry.md — jsou generovane
- NECOMMITUJ secrets, credentials, .env soubory
- NEPRACUJ v Apps Script editoru jako source of truth
- NEVYTVAREJ soubory v root slozce — pouzij spravny adresar

## Behavioral Rules

- Read file before editing
- NEVER create files unless necessary
- NEVER commit .env files
- Keep files under 500 lines

## File Organization

- `/apps-script` — Google Apps Script backend
- `/crm-frontend` — Next.js CRM frontend
- `/docs` — Kanonicka dokumentace
- `/docs/archive` — Historicke/referencni dokumenty
- `/docs/30-task-records` — Evidence zmenovych tasku
- `/scripts/docs` — Dokumentacni automatizace
- `/offers` — Obchodni nabidky
- `/scripts` — Utility skripty

## Build & Test

```bash
# Frontend build
cd crm-frontend && npm run build

# Doc validation
node scripts/docs/check-doc-sync.mjs

# Generate changelog + registry
node scripts/docs/build-changelog.mjs
node scripts/docs/build-task-registry.mjs

# New task record
node scripts/docs/create-task-record.mjs A2 "Task title"
```

## Security

- NEVER hardcode API keys or secrets
- NEVER commit .env files
- Always validate user input at system boundaries

## Definition of Done

Task je HOTOV az kdyz:
1. **Code done:** tsc OK, build OK, no secrets
2. **Task record:** vytvoreny/aktualizovany v docs/30-task-records/
3. **Docs done:** prislusne kanonicke docs aktualizovany
4. **Generated docs:** changelog + task registry regenerovany
5. **Validation:** check-doc-sync.mjs — 0 fail
